spec.question_description:
For field-notice-driven ordering (e.g. FN74306 on 4HG-FLEX). YAML list of {location, fpd} items in required order. Each is upgraded and polled until CURRENT before the next runs. Example:
  - { location: "0/1", fpd: "Sunstreaker" }
  - { location: "0/1", fpd: "TAMFW-Sunstreaker" }
  - { location: "0/1", fpd: "Primary-BIOS" }
Leave as [] to skip sequenced stage and go straight to bulk upgrade.
